nodes.text: Jat Kaa's Coolers was a company owned by the Lurmen male Jat Kaa, who hailed from the planet Mygeeto. He imported beverages to the Outer Rim planet Batuu and sold them throughout Black Spire Outpost. His workers, R-series astromech droids purchased from Droid Depot, operated drink carts throughout the outpost to sell the beverages Coca-Cola, Diet Coke, Sprite, and Dasani to travelers and local Batuuans.
